<h1>Youngest director</h1>

<% youngest_director = Director.where.not(dob: nil).order(dob: :desc).first %>

<% if youngest_director %>
  <p>The youngest director in our dataset right now is <a href="/directors/<%= youngest_director.id %>"><%= youngest_director.name %></a>, born on <%= youngest_director.dob.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>.</p>
<% else %>
  <p>No directors with a date of birth found.</p>
<% end %>

<p>(<a href="http://strftime.net/" target="_blank">http://strftime.net/</a> is handy for putting together the formatting strings for the <code>.strftime</code> method.)</p>

